channel.title: RetroScape - Going out with a bang!
channel.description:
[center][URL=http://img94.imageshack.us/i/retrobanner.gif/][IMG]http://img94.imageshack.us/img94/8651/retrobanner.gif[/img][/URL] I'm 3 r k on Run3-Server NO ONE ELSE, I HAVN'T GOT ANY OTHER ACCOUNTS, DON'T POST THIS ANYWHERE ELSE WITHOUT MY PERMISSION OR GIVING ME CREDITS! [u][b]Links[/b][/u] [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?q7l453ctxwf432s]Server[/url] [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?le7dcn0beqka5bn]Client[/url] [u][b]Background info[/b][/u] RetroScape was a Server developed by me and some others. The source I used is Impact V2.0, which IS better then Project Insanity, stability and networking wise. I loved every minute developing this Server and it was great fun! I hope you guys and girls use this as a base because it's much better then the normal PI. Most items were added in the correct slots, but if some arn't just add them in Item.java. X Entinity X Exion Ix Soulcist xI RuneSpace. I'd like to thank; Sanity Supporters MoparScape Mimmel Core Graham And anyone else who wants to be thanked. [u][b]Features[/b][/u] [ul][li]Webclient Playable[/li] [li]Fullscreen Playable[/li] [li]Vps hosted[/li] [li]$250 start off[/li] [li]Decent pHp Forums[/li][/ul] [u]Update log[/u]
